While she saw at Devilduel typed the button Vamprah was thinkling 
again about her future... 

What'd hapen with her? What would happen when Zardus knew about her 
prencence? What was going on with Darkfate? Would Daimond tell about 
her precense at Zardus???

"By the pit... If I'm in danger how will I survive?"asked herself 
inside her mind
